data.description: Open house Sun Dec 17th 1-3 PM. 3.3% VA assumable loan. Are you Looking for a semi private yard and raised bed garden? This 3 bed, 2 bath, 2 car, walkout ranch sits on a semi private lot that  backs to trees. The home has a split bedroom plan. Primary bedroom has a large walk-in closet and full bath. Bedrooms 2 and 3 are split by a second full bath and adjacent to laundry. Cozy family room has had carpets cleaned in Nov. 2023 and has a fireplace to enjoy, during the upcoming winter nights. Kitchen /dining walks out  to deck that overlooks back yard. The lighted, enclosed and raised bed garden ,located behind the property, in the common area, has been beautifully maintained by past homeowners. There is a large partially finished walkout basement with new carpet installed Oct. 2023 and large storage area with  a bathroom rough-in for future completion. Shelving in storage area for convenience. Make this the first home on your list to see. Pre-inspected Oct. 2023.
